{"tid":2033193,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「是咁的，我係PPRB，我將會咁拆解偷水一事」","createTime":"2020-05-24T13:25:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T17:52:07.000Z","uid":37959,"like":14,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"666cd1faf4509203a015cddc7e15067f92159447","tid":2033193,"uid":37959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:25:42.000Z","msg":"影片拍到的：<br />\n1. 有警員走入店舖拿走水後，沒有付款<br />\n2. PPRB及後到場付款<br />\n<br />\n事實經過：<br />\n1. 店員聲稱請警員飲水，為警察打氣，警員才入去拿水走<br />\n2. PPRB事後到場感謝店員，並付款<br />\n<br />\n相信呢段時間，便利店同埋店員都會被威脅同施壓，要跟以上解釋出街<br />\n<br />\n所以唔好怪便利店（唔知佢黃定藍），就算佢最後點解釋都好，唔好攻擊間野，佢先係受害者，比人偷水仲要比人威脅返，要攻擊就開盡火力攻擊班狗"},{"pid":"cc6eaa491cc4acfadb2103348d59a0388ffc361a","tid":2033193,"uid":37959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:26:13.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"0f0e83b78e7a5ee58cd5c152db8dd8fa3c3bc631","tid":2033193,"uid":37959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:26:25.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"9860ae62a810564c01bb0eb906b67b8d31d7ff63","tid":2033193,"uid":240664,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:27:27.000Z","msg":"犯法就係犯法，一定要負責"},{"pid":"df4ced48914eb316961d10f4fb84d47538ab271e","tid":2033193,"uid":37959,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:27:59.000Z","msg":"出面仲focus係OK點解釋，佢屌狗既，咪當bonus，相反就算佢幫狗既，都唔好怪佢，事實係點，大家心水清，佢都係比人威脅"},{"pid":"0398bed6dd3bd08cef0c4e0ada81a5fb0c68c017","tid":2033193,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:28:25.000Z","msg":"已訓斥（完）"},{"pid":"39bbced66e913fb323e21cccb26f48abb9305763","tid":2033193,"uid":228437,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:29:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咁你又講後數</span></strong>"},{"pid":"0da259da90581e500e86ef2e9565dbd1d6959a9a","tid":2033193,"uid":73350,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:31:03.000Z","msg":"接受他人饋贈個刻已經係賄賂"},{"pid":"7a4b983